s://wordpress.org/plugins/cachify/\">Cachify</a>, which was very popular in Germany until the developer abandoned Cachify) is well-written, simple and efficient. :-)</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ao_pagecache.png\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-10558 alignnone\" src=\"http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ao_pagecache-300x180.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"180\" srcset=\"http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ao_pagecache-300x180.png 300w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ao_pagecache-1024x613.png 1024w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ao_pagecache-624x374.png 624w, http://blog.futtta.be/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/ao_pagecache.png 1119w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a></p>\n<p>No plans to release this though. Or do you think I should?</p>\n<div class=\'yarpp-related-rss\'>\n<p>Possibly related twitterless twaddle:<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2016/05/18/quick-keycdns-cache-enabler-test/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Quick KeyCDN&#8217;s Cache Enabler test\">Quick KeyCDN&#8217;s Cache Enabler test </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2016/03/15/why-would-you-still-be-on-php-5-2/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Why would you still be on PHP 5.2?\">Why would you still be on PHP 5.2? </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2017/08/11/loading-webfonts-just-for-a-title-switch-to-svg-instead/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Loading webfonts just for a title? Switch to SVG instead.\">Loading webfonts just for a title? Switch to SVG instead. </a></li>\n</ul></p>\n</div>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/futtta_autoptimize/~4/UZAs4GkzvM0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:84:\"https://blog.futtta.be/2017/11/16/small-exper