baOLWjpc\">on YouTube</a>.</p>\n<div class=\'yarpp-related-rss\'>\n<p>Possibly related twitterless twaddle:<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2010/05/18/lite-youtube-embeds-in-wordpress/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Lite YouTube Embeds in WordPress\">Lite YouTube Embeds in WordPress </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2010/05/25/lovin-the-wordpress-plugin-ecosystem/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Lovin&#8217; the WordPress plugin ecosystem\">Lovin&#8217; the WordPress plugin ecosystem </a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.futtta.be/2010/06/16/embedding-html5-youtube-video-with-wp-youtube-lyte/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Embedding HTML5 YouTube video with WP YouTube Lyte\">Embedding HTML5 YouTube video with WP YouTube Lyte </a></li>\n</ul></p>\n</div>\n<img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/futtta_wordpress/~4/CsU1_E4k5sg\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:75:\"https://blog.futtta.be/2018/03/07/long-overdue-wp-youtube-lyte-update/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:42:\"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0\";a:1:{s:8:\"origLink\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://blog.futtta.be/2018/03/07/long-overdue-wp-youtube-lyte-update/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:51:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s